{"tid":783289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵：海軍商場於沙中綫工程前已沉降","createTime":"2018-08-17T12:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T12:59:28.000Z","uid":37554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"872b9e6b765c69ab2c48a6115979c17a619d414c","tid":783289,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:07:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】灣仔分域碼頭海軍商場出現多處明顯裂紋 ，被質疑與沙中綫工程沉降有關。港鐵指，海軍商場早在沙中綫工程前已沉降，強調除了鐵路項目外，其他工程也會引致沉降。<br />\n<br />\n灣仔分域碼頭海軍商場在銅鑼灣避風塘至金鐘站隧道上方牆身有多條明顯裂縫。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵稱，於二零一四年六月勘測海軍商場時，發現該處早於沙中綫工程前已出現沉降，當時灣仔北亦進行其他基建工程，強調地基、挖掘或隧道工程引致沉降並非罕見。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指，開始隧道鑽挖前已作預防措施，有關工程一直在安全情況下進行，港鐵曾經為商場作三次樓宇影響評估，確認結構完整，政府部門八月視察時無發現明顯結構安全問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=316893&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D316893%26refer%3D&d=NHbw2oie4etD3AzW2Rykb%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=1e67b6c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D316893%26refer%3D&h=a2bc8749\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=316893&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180816/large/1534408091_8298.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180816%2Flarge%2F1534408091_8298.jpg&h=8c49e122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180816/large/1534392140_d0c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180816%2Flarge%2F1534392140_d0c5.jpg&h=21dde666&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a311b89093f900a5240d6e891c06f14c16e71b08","tid":783289,"uid":199590,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"收皮啦! 點講都好佢都一定有份加劇個情況! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37359b88ff1f3454fef4